cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR. 

The paper focuses on emotion recognition from facial expressions using deep learning, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of deep learning models for joint super-resolution and recognition also falls under multimedia (cs.MM). The proposed max-mix training strategy and the evaluation of the framework on a benchmark dataset demonstrate the use of machine learning techniques (cs.LG, cs.AI). Finally, the paper also discusses the impact of network bandwidth on recognition performance, which relates to information retrieval (cs.IR).
